62:        "_NOTE_MEMORY_DB_PATH": "createChildEnv() pins the advisor child's embedder-pointer resolution (which DB's active_embedder_* row gets read) to this package's own skill-graph.sqlite. An ambient MEMORY_DB_PATH â€” including one set for mk-spec-memory's own unrelated use of that same name â€” is never honored as an override, since that would silently misroute the advisor's embedder selection to spec-memory's database (the exact bug this pin fixed). Tests/CI only: MK_SKILL_ADVISOR_MEMORY_DB_PATH overrides the pin. See db_path_policy.md Â§4.",
64:        "_NOTE_DOC_TRIGGERS": "Opt-in doc-frontmatter harvest: skill_graph_scan ingests references/assets trigger_phrases into skill_docs and advisor_recommend returns matchedDocs pointers (dampened derived-lane signal). Default-off in code; enabled for this repo. Unset/false to roll back.",
